<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">مثل قوله تعالى:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{أَنْ تُبْسَلَ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[الأنعام: ٧٠]</span> قيل: تحبس،<span style="color:#006d98"> وقيل:</span> ترتهن.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وقوله تعالى:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{وَمَا مَسَّنَا مِنْ لُغُوبٍ}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[ق: ٣٨]</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">قال ابن عباس ومجاهد:</span> نصب.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وقال ابن زيد:</span> عناء.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وقال سفيان:</span> سآمة. <span style="color:#707070">[٦٢]</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
